title: 6 Creative Recipes Using 1 Can of Sardines !! (Part 2)
description:
Part 1 : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BsvxQ01Oy8k Canned Sardines deserve your LOVE ! Sardines Kurma Curry, Fried Sardines in Chimichurri sauce or even Sardines Spread rolls... SO many recipes you can make with a can of Sardines.
